item.title: CVE-2021-3821|2024-08-03T17:09:09.605Z -- hp%20inc. -- hp%20futuresmart
item.description: A potential security vulnerability has been identified for certain HP multifunction printers (MFPs). The vulnerability may lead to Denial of Service when running HP Workpath solutions on potentially affected products.
